{"word":"G5152 - τρίστεγον - trístegon - tris'-teg-on - Third loft","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τρίστεγον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">trístegon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tris'-teg-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Third loft</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மூன்று மாடி - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"having three roofs or stories"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G5140 - τρεῖς - treîs - trice/5140\">G5140</a> and <a href=\"#/G4721 - στέγη - stégē - steg'-ay/4721\">G4721</a> as noun; a <i>third roof</i> (<i>story</i>): - third loft.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5140/5140\">G5140</a>, <a href=\"#/G5151/5151\">G5151</a>, <a href=\"#/G5152/5152\">G5152</a>, <a href=\"#/G5153/5153\">G5153</a>, <a href=\"#/G5154/5154\">G5154</a>"}]}